title: MisterMusic Show 325 - new indie,alternative,rock radio
description:
MisterMusic Show 325 - 192kbps MP3 Stereo- [2 hours]-



On this episode of the MisterMusic Show, new music from Stars, The New Pornographers, and Bush.
Plus a big hit from 19 years ago is the 'Oldie of the Week'. A song that was number 1 in October 1995.

It's over 5 decades of classic hits mixed with new indie and alternative music.

The MisterMusic Show is broadcast weekly and heard globally on Rock XS Radio.
